# Deployment

- Staging: branch `develop` → `baseer-staging` / `baseer-api-staging`
- Production: tag `v*` → `baseer` / `baseer-api`
- R2: `docket-documents-staging` / `docket-documents` — never public; presigned URLs only via `lib/r2.ts`
- Cookie domain must match app host for Pages/Workers session sharing
- Document ops in `docs/DEPLOYMENT.md` and `docs/RUNBOOK.md`
